query_list: SELECT wuc_max_count.Work_Unit_Code, max(wucs_w_duplicates_2.WUC_Narrative) WUC_Narrative, wuc_max_count.Count FROM (SELECT Work_Unit_Code, max(Count) Count FROM (SELECT Work_Unit_Code, WUC_Narrative, count(*) Count FROM compiled_c130_remis_data GROUP BY  Work_Unit_Code, WUC_Narrative) wucs_w_duplicates GROUP BY  Work_Unit_Code) wuc_max_count JOIN (SELECT Work_Unit_Code, WUC_Narrative, count(*) Count FROM compiled_c130_remis_data GROUP BY  Work_Unit_Code, WUC_Narrative) wucs_w_duplicates_2 ON wuc_max_count.Work_Unit_Code = wucs_w_duplicates_2.Work_Unit_Code and wuc_max_count.count = wucs_w_duplicates_2.count GROUP BY  Work_Unit_Code, Count ORDER BY  wuc_max_count.Work_Unit_Code

query_list: SELECT On_Component_Serial_Number, On_Component_Part_Number, Equipment_Designator, Serial_Number, Geographic_Location, Performing_Geographic_Location, Transaction_Date, Start_Time, Work_Center_Code, When_Discovered_Code, How_Malfunction_Code, compiled_c130_remis_data.Action_Taken_Code, Type_Maintenance_Code, compiled_c130_remis_data.Current_Operating_Time, Component_Position_Number, Corrective_Narrative, Discrepancy_Narrative, Work_Center_Event_Narrative, compiled_c130_remis_data.On_Work_Order_Key, compiled_c130_remis_data.On_Maint_Action_Key, compiled_c130_remis_data.Work_Center_Event_Identifier, compiled_c130_remis_data.Sequence_Number, compiled_c130_remis_data.Work_Order_Number FROM compiled_c130_remis_data JOIN split_r_and_multi_pos ON compiled_c130_remis_data.On_Work_Order_Key = split_r_and_multi_pos.On_Work_Order_Key AND compiled_c130_remis_data.On_Maint_Action_Key = split_r_and_multi_pos.On_Maint_Action_Key AND compiled_c130_remis_data.Work_Center_Event_Identifier = split_r_and_multi_pos.Work_Center_Event_Identifier AND compiled_c130_remis_data.Sequence_Number = split_r_and_multi_pos.Sequence_Number AND compiled_c130_remis_data.Work_Order_Number = split_r_and_multi_pos.Work_Order_Number JOIN current_operating_time ON compiled_c130_remis_data.On_Work_Order_Key = current_operating_time.On_Work_Order_Key AND compiled_c130_remis_data.On_Maint_Action_Key = current_operating_time.On_Maint_Action_Key AND compiled_c130_remis_data.Work_Center_Event_Identifier = current_operating_time.Work_Center_Event_Identifier AND compiled_c130_remis_data.Sequence_Number = current_operating_time.Sequence_Number AND compiled_c130_remis_data.Work_Order_Number = current_operating_time.Work_Order_Number
